query_always_use_default_position

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_always_use_default_position -  This method sets the always the flag to always use the default position.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_always_use_default_position()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the always use default position flag
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the always the flag to always use the default position.
If this is set then rooms cannot override the position message which is
displayed by the object.
.EP

